name: Jorney To The Past.2 (Sign)
description:
There will always a sign so we don't get lost, a sign that keep us prepare for all the possibilities that occur in every path of our lives.

Selalu ada penunjuk arah agar kita tak tersesat, sebuah pertanda agar kita tetap mempersiapkan segala kemungkinan yang terjadi di setiap jalan hidup kita.
